briefdescription.para: Represents type codes that are used by parts of the Haiku API.

detaileddescription.para: The type codes all refer to a specified type, except one: B_ANY_TYPE can refer to literally any type. This type could be used in case you send or receive data of which you don't know the type, but you want to send or receive it anyway.
